ENTRY            41731   20260206   20260319   20260319       4226
SUBENT        41731001   20260206   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                 11         20
TITLE      Experimental determination of delayed neutron group
           yields from thermal fission of 233U and 235U
AUTHOR     (A.N.Gudkov,V.M.Zhivun,V.V.Kovalenko,A.B.Koldobsky,
           S.V.Krivasheev)
REFERENCE  ((J,YK,,(2),56,1986)=
           (R,INDC(CCP)-260,56,1986)) In Russian
INSTITUTE  (4RUSMIF)
SAMPLE      Samples of ~1 microgram in polyethylene containers
FACILITY   (REAC,4RUSMIF) IRT-2000 reactor
INC-SOURCE (REAC)
INC-SPECT   Thermal neutron flux 4.10**13 n/(cm2*sec)
METHOD     (ACTIV,GSPEC) 16 cycles of irradiation and counting for
           each sample. Cycle time 640 sec, measurement time not
           less than 580 sec.
DETECTOR   (PROPC) 14 SNM-11 counters for delayed neutron
           detection. Radiometer efficiency 7.01+-0.64 %.
           (GELI) For counting of fission events.
HISTORY    (20210125C)  M.M.
           (20260206A) Subent 003 was corrected.
            STATUS was updated for new rules.
ENDBIB              20
COMMON               1          3
EN-DUMMY
EV
 0.0253
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           27
SUBENT        41731002   20260206   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                  5         12
REACTION   (92-U-235(N,F),DL/GRP,NU,,SPA)
MONITOR    (92-U-235(N,F),DL,NU) For absolute efficiency of
           delayed neutron radiometer.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Type of uncertainty is not explained in the
           article.
REL-REF    (A,,V.M.Sluchevskaya+,J,YK,,(3/38),29,1980) =
           (A,,V.M.Sluchevskaya+,R,INDC(CCP)-156,29,1980)
            Review of experiments and recom. data.
STATUS     (TABLE,,A.N.Gudkov+,R,INDC(CCP)-260,56,1986) Table 1.
           (COREL,41730002) In 41730.002 U-235 sample of
            2.08+-0.01 microgram was measured for normalization
            purpose, together with Th-229 sample.
